text: Okan Yilmaz (born 13 October 1997) is an Austrian footballer who plays for SK Vorwärts Steyr. ==Personal life== Born in Austria, Yilmaz is of Turkish descent. ==References== ==External links== *Okan Yilmaz at ÖFB Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian footballers Category:Austrian people of Turkish descent Category:FC Wacker Innsbruck players Category:SK Vorwärts Steyr players Category:Austrian Football Second League players Category:Austrian Regionalliga players Category:Association football midfielders
